<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.6.8">
<l>ēviḷaṅ kaṉṉik kāki yimaiyavar kōṉaic ceṟṟu</l>
<l>kāvaḷaṅ kaṭiti ṟuttuk kaṟpakaṅ koṇṭu pōntāy</l>
<l>pūvaḷam poḻilkaḷ cūḻnta purantaraṉ ceyta nāṅkaik</l>
<l>kāvaḷam pāṭi mēya kaṇṇaṉē kaḷaika ṇīyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who, tormenting the celestials’ king</l>
<l rend="indent">for the sake of the young girl who demanded [it],</l>
<l>Quickly ruining the garden, carried off the kalpaka tree,</l>
<l>Kaṇṇaṉ who dwells in the hamlet of Kāvaḷam in Nāṅkai,</l>
<l rend="indent">which the fort-breaker established,</l>
<l>Surrounded by fertile groves of flowers, only you are [our] refuge.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
